# ============================================================================
# PHILOSOPHY OF EXCLUSION
# ============================================================================
#
# This .gitignore embodies a fundamental principle: 
# Version control should preserve intent, not artifact.
#
# We include:
# - Source code (the thoughts)
# - Configuration templates (the patterns)
# - Documentation (the explanations)
# - Tests (the validations)
#
# We exclude:
# - Generated outputs (reproducible artifacts)
# - Secrets (private knowledge)
# - Environment-specific debris (local context)
# - Tool artifacts (means, not ends)
#
# Every exclusion is an act of curation, choosing what deserves 
# to travel through time and what should remain local to the moment.
#
# This file is itself a kind of prompt chain - each pattern
# anticipates a future possibility and prepares a response.
# ============================================================================